pullrequest.title: Don't use cmake cache for auto-generated header strings

content.raw: Not sure about the CI builds, but it built fine on my local copy both with CMake 3.10 and 3.15 \(after applying the workaround for DART from [#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2663/build-error-gazebo9-and-dart](#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2663/build-error-gazebo9-and-dart) \).
